# Cloud Run Optimization Notes:
# This .dockerignore is optimized for:
# - Apple Silicon development with OrbStack/Podman
# - Google Cloud Run AMD64 deployment
# - Minimal build context for faster uploads
# - Maximum layer caching efficiency
